Test 1: Chained calls
append('Hello') -> 'Hello'
append(' ') -> 'Hello '
append('World') -> 'Hello World'
Result: 'Hello World'

Test 2: Mixed chaining
append('First') -> 'First'
appendLine(' Line') -> length 0
append('Second') -> 'First Line
Second'
appendLine(' Line') -> length 0
Result: 'First Line
Second Line
'

Test 3: Chain with clear
append('Temp') -> 'Temp'
clear() -> empty
append('New') -> 'New'
append(' Content') -> 'New Content'
Result: 'New Content'
